ascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xmz1665703273141.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xmz1665703273141.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xmz1665703273141\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      /cln\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Clean up components by deleting orphan definitions in the component.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xmz1665703273141__section_w2976ab1b5b1_w2977ab1b5_w2978ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xmz1665703273141__p_d148124e1_d148125e1_d148126e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/cln</span> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Component</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xmz1665703273141__section_w2979ab1b5b3_w2980ab1b5_w2981ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d961730e63\">\n                  \n Use With\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xmz1665703273141__d6270e20\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">ide</span>—Uniface IDE</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xmz1665703273141__section_w2982ab1b5b5_w2983ab1b5_w2984ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d961730e75\">\n                  \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xmz1665703273141__p_d148136e1_d148137e1_d148138e1\">Clean up the named component. If you omit <var class=\"keyword varname\">Component</var>, all components are cleaned up. You can use wildcard characters to specify a group of components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xmz1665703273141__section_w2985ab1b5b7_w2986ab1b5_w2987ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d961730e87\">Example: /cln </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xmz1665703273141__p_d148142e1_d148143e1_d148144e1\">The following example cleans up all components:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">/cln *</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533801\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533801\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "/cln Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 22, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 /cln Clean up components by deleting orphan definitions in the component. /cln { Component } Use With ide —Uniface IDE Description Clean up the named component. If you omit Component , all components are cleaned up. You can use wildcard characters to specify a group of components. Example: /cln The following example cleans up all components: /cln * Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}